{"tid":1139560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（打工妹）今日返工可能做錯嘢 應唔應該同老闆交代清楚定繼續忍瞞？","createTime":"2019-05-05T10:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T20:17:22.000Z","uid":2104,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2f30eb5404e7637cee23602dc7e65c127fd4c8","tid":1139560,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">是咁的...<br />\n話說我喺深水埗一間原材料化工行做實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時都係幫手計下重量數下貨對下單咁 都唔算粗重嘢<br />\n咁今日原本執貨嗰個長工屋企有啲所以事請咗日假<br />\n今日全日都係得我同另一個長工睇舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時朝早就最忙 今日都唔例外<br />\n好多客都會喺早上過嚟提貨 <br />\n佢哋啲單通常都會早一兩日落定 然後我哋就會執定等佢哋第二日嚟拎<br />\n有時都會有街客散客嚟到即場買 <br />\n今日就喺最忙嗰陣 有個街客要買嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢個街客都算熟客 一星期嚟一次到<br />\n每次都買硝酸鉀 平時就長工執開<br />\n咁今日忙 老闆就叫我如果識執嘅就幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我始終都係新人 邊樣打邊樣都只係大概分到 唔係好有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部分呢類原材料都係白白灰灰咁 鬼認到咩<br />\n賣完俾佢之後我睇返單同貨名先發現我俾錯鎂佢<br />\n我驚個客之後發現返嚟嘈 又驚老闆點貨發現錯數<br />\n不過好彩好多出入單都會經我手 其實我只要做下手腳就冇問題<br />\n但係好驚最後教係爆鑊 點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f9f421b69559e80a1c3b6c467f86194ad410544b","tid":1139560,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"係咪on9 個客擺明實會返黎退貨啦 你自定首啦 仲問"},{"pid":"211b239e2146c11537ff65e21e92d4a33986443d","tid":1139560,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"少事化大  完"},{"pid":"f429a78cab837de9cca9565142bb6be68dd027bb","tid":1139560,"uid":143192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"鎂銀灰色架"},{"pid":"2703be84a92b8911cee1f473e4cc4267357cf901","tid":1139560,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9f421b69559e80a1c3b6c467f86194ad410544b","tid":1139560,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"係咪on9 個客擺明實會返黎退貨啦 你自定首啦 仲問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"好驚會俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16926d3b120ec488176672b57d19eae5365bb2d7","tid":1139560,"uid":58445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"比錯野好閒 試下打比個客返黎換 <br />\n佢唔嘈就神不g鬼不覺"},{"pid":"4a078519215ae74e70744a872f10cc2d131777b0","tid":1139560,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"應該即刻講 叫個客黎換"},{"pid":"9f5ae366c11cface302955ff3710c30cbee61107","tid":1139560,"uid":172278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"好有潮文feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768ae4d2c4e2af16c809a670083e4c07cfd452d6","tid":1139560,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT